org.cojen.classfile

Class MethodInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cojen.classfile.MethodInfo

  • public class MethodInfo
extends Object
    This class corresponds to the method_info data structure as defined in The Java Virtual Machine Specification. Call newCodeBuilder() to obtain a CodeBuilder instance for adding instructions to this method.
    Author:
    Brian S O'Neill
    See Also:
    ClassFile, CodeBuilder

      • newCodeBuilder

        public CodeBuilder newCodeBuilder(boolean saveLineNumberInfo,
                         boolean saveLocalVariableInfo)
        Returns a new CodeBuilder instance for adding instructions to this method.
        Parameters:
        saveLineNumberInfo - When set false, all calls to CodeBuilder.mapLineNumber(int) are ignored. By default, this value is true.
        saveLocalVariableInfo - When set true, all local variable usage information is saved in the ClassFile. By default, this value is false.
